## The Lab-Grown Certification Question at 3 Carats

In our dataset you can see an interesting divergence:

- **IGI 3ct D-VVS1 Ideal**: $7,000
- **GIA 3ct D-VVS1 Excellent**: $7,340
- **GCAL 3ct D-VVS1 Ideal**: $20,100
- **GIA 3ct D-FL Excellent**: $27,700

The GCAL and upper-tier GIA prices are outliers — they include extra certification prestige and, in some cases, additional stone quality screening that IGI alone does not mandate. For lab-grown diamonds, IGI is the industry standard certification, and the IGI stones offer the best value by a wide margin. Read more about certification differences in our [GIA certified round diamond guide](/gia-certified-round-diamond){target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"}.

